https://hostname:5000/api/v1/confirm @login_required
https://hostname:5000/api/v1/confirm/<token> @login_required
https://hostname:5000/api/v1/change-password (POST)
https://hostname:5000/api/v1/reset (POST)
https://hostname:5000/api/v1/reset/<token> (POST)
https://hostname:5000/api/v1/change-email (POST)
https://hostname:5000/api/v1/change-email/<token> (POST)
https://hostname:5000/api/v1/token (GET)

